Defeat Tarkrîp Shooters in western Nan Wathren ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Orcs have taken over the canyons of Nan Wathren, and should be driven out.

In stepping to the edge of the gorge of Nan Wathren, you see that it has fallen utterly into the hands of the Tarkrîp Orcs.

A difficult and treacherous path lies beyond the bridge.

You should defeat Orcs in Nan Wathren, but bring companions with you wherever you go from this point forward, for it is deadly within.

<rgb=#FF0000>Small fellowship recommended.</rgb>
